<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3101] bin assembly doesn&apos;t include -tests or -source jars</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3101</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the bin assembly tries to include the hbase-VERSION-tests.jar but there&apos;s a typo &quot;test&quot; instead of &quot;tests&quot; in the assembly descriptor, so it doesn&apos;t do so. Also, I think we should probably ship the -sources jar even in the -bin assembly - it&apos;s useful for people to point their IDE at it to get API javadocs, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12476938">HBASE-3101</key>
            <summary>bin assembly doesn&apos;t include -tests or -source jars</summary>
